    <svcsubproc>
        <title>Fire Extinguisher</title>
        <para>Fire Extinguishers are supplied and mounted on all school buses. The location may vary depending on the
            seating arrangement, step well and driver control configurations and state requirements (
            <hotlnk xrefid="f4700549">Fig. 49, Item 1</hotlnk>).
        </para>
